{
  "name": "CP Fleet Commander — Estate Agent",
  "nodes": [
    {
      "parameters": {
        "content": "## 🎖️ Check Point Fleet Commander\n**One chat. Your whole Check Point estate.** Ask anything — management, Gaia, gateway CLI, threat prevention & emulation, reputation, HTTPS inspection, logs, cpinfo, docs — this agent routes to the right MCP tool through the Docker MCP Gateway.",
        "width": 1420,
        "height": 120,
        "color": 5
      },
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote",
      "typeVersion": 1,
      "position": [
        -140,
        -300
      ],
      "id": "d22eea71-bc48-5134-808e-bd7cd114e4c4",
      "name": "Banner"
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "content": "### 💬 Try these\n- Which gateways are in my estate and are their policies installed?\n- Any drops from 10.1.1.222 in the last 24h — and what's that IP's reputation?\n- Draft (don't publish) a rule blocking Facebook for the Guest network\n- Summarize the strictest Threat Prevention profile\n\n### ⚙️ How it works\n**One endpoint, every tool.** Calls ride the Docker MCP Gateway (`mcp-gateway:8080/mcp`, Bearer auth) which aggregates the whole Check Point MCP fleet — a curated 113-tool core across every domain (the model API caps tools at 128).\n\n### 🧠 Models\nAzure OpenAI **gpt-5.4** is the wired default; Ollama (local), Gemini 2.5 Pro, GPT-5.1 and Claude Opus 4.8 are one click away.",
        "width": 460,
        "height": 640,
        "color": 7
      },
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote",
      "typeVersion": 1,
      "position": [
        -660,
        -300
      ],
      "id": "a29322e7-9d6c-5236-856d-86dd7242f0fc",
      "name": "Guide"
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "public": true,
        "initialMessages": "🎖️ I'm the **Check Point Fleet Commander** — I operate your entire estate through one MCP gateway: management, Gaia, gateway CLI, threat prevention & emulation, reputation, HTTPS inspection, logs, cpinfo and docs.\n\n**Try one of these:**\n- Which gateways are in my estate and are their policies installed?\n- Any drops from 10.1.1.222 in the last 24h — and that IP's reputation?\n- Summarize the strictest Threat Prevention profile",
        "options": {
          "responseMode": "lastNode",
          "title": "🎖️ CP Fleet Commander",
          "subtitle": "One chat for your whole Check Point estate.",
          "inputPlaceholder": "Ask anything about your Check Point estate…"
        }
      },
      "type": "@n8n/n8n-nodes-langchain.chatTrigger",
      "typeVersion": 1.1,
      "position": [
        -140,
        60
      ],
      "id": "3cef2949-36bd-5849-8754-2fc108e12191",
      "name": "When chat message received",
